wdi2-SP.POP.TOTL.MA.ZS.def: Male population is the percentage of the population that is male. Population is based on the de facto definition of population, which counts all residents regardless of legal status or citizenship.
wdi2-SP.POP.TOTL.MA.ZS.name: Population
wdi2-SP.POP.TOTL.MA.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates based on age/sex distributions of United Nations Population Division's World Population Prospects: 2019 Revision.
